des:
Play an science fiction-themed story with sound effects and prompts. Get ready for laughs and giggles.
Understand the way's of the Lord in this science fiction story, if you pray to the Lord, maybe you will realize the virus he has for you,, more than human enhancement technologies, viruses are more than pathogens, they are race, vaccines and the Lord's Way. Understand his plan for humanity and a vaccine for the rest of the planet, the living one. Do you see the need to return to the living?
